title: Baked Good

title: Rock Sample
description: A rough, irregularly shaped rock with a layered texture. The rock has a mix of gray and yellowish hues, indicating possible mineral content.

title: Ancient Artifact

title: Fossilized Dinosaur Coprolite

title: Collection of Rocks
description: A small pile of various rocks, including a smooth, rounded stone on top, a flat, orange-brown rock, and several irregularly shaped gray and light-colored stones.

title: Granite Rock
description: A piece of granite rock displaying a speckled pattern of black and white minerals, showcasing its crystalline texture.
